(20, 'Custom Mobile Tracker', 'mobile-custom', NULL, NULL, '<div class=\"container\">\r\n<h2 class=\"text-center\" style=\"margin-top: 100px; margin-bottom: 30px\">Custom Mobile Tracker</h2>\r\n\r\n<p paraeid=\"{999e0793-ec05-4bb2-a130-3feca89d0f59}{169}\" paraid=\"1185048548\">Are you looking for Customized Mobile&nbsp;Application to sync your Smart Phone&nbsp;with CRM?&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p paraeid=\"{999e0793-ec05-4bb2-a130-3feca89d0f59}{179}\" paraid=\"303186966\">We provide end to end functional mobile application solution which can be synced with CRM like Bitrix24,&nbsp;Zoho,&nbsp;HubSpot&nbsp;and&nbsp;Vitiger&nbsp;etc. Our expert team of mobile application development and CRM engineers&nbsp;can provide solution&nbsp;to transfer your calls, SMS, call logs, call records,&nbsp;add&nbsp;comments, schedule tasks, meetings and number of other requirements aligned with CRM of your choice.&nbsp;We are expert of developing hybrid react-native mobile application development based on the business requirement.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p paraeid=\"{999e0793-ec05-4bb2-a130-3feca89d0f59}{211}\" paraid=\"72744157\">Our Customized Mobile Application offers following Features:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol role=\"list\" start=\"1\">\r\n	<li aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-level=\"1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-font=\"Times New Roman\" data-leveltext=\"%1.\" data-listid=\"1\" role=\"listitem\">\r\n	<p paraeid=\"{999e0793-ec05-4bb2-a130-3feca89d0f59}{221}\" paraid=\"619605813\">Recording important calls and pushing them in CRM.&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<ol role=\"list\" start=\"2\">\r\n	<li aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-level=\"1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-font=\"Times New Roman\" data-leveltext=\"%1.\" data-listid=\"1\" role=\"listitem\">\r\n	<p paraeid=\"{999e0793-ec05-4bb2-a130-3feca89d0f59}{228}\" paraid=\"877813744\">Generating leads based on incoming calls.&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<ol role=\"list\" start=\"3\">\r\n	<li aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-level=\"1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-font=\"Times New Roman\" data-leveltext=\"%1.\" data-listid=\"1\" role=\"listitem\">\r\n	<p paraeid=\"{999e0793-ec05-4bb2-a130-3feca89d0f59}{235}\" paraid=\"2115219376\">Call Duration, Location Tracking, Call Alerts and Notifications.&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<ol role=\"list\" start=\"4\">\r\n	<li aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-level=\"1\" data-aria-posinset=\"4\" data-font=\"Times New Roman\" data-leveltext=\"%1.\" data-listid=\"1\" role=\"listitem\">\r\n	<p paraeid=\"{999e0793-ec05-4bb2-a130-3feca89d0f59}{242}\" paraid=\"1290227504\">Capable of working in offline mode to not miss any critical business information&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<ol role=\"list\" start=\"5\">\r\n	<li aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-level=\"1\" data-aria-posinset=\"5\" data-font=\"Times New Roman\" data-leveltext=\"%1.\" data-listid=\"1\" role=\"listitem\">\r\n	<p paraeid=\"{999e0793-ec05-4bb2-a130-3feca89d0f59}{249}\" paraid=\"279496355\">Team collaboration through GSM&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"space-70\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"cta-skin\">\r\n<div class=\"container text-center\">\r\n<h2>ARE YOU LOOKING FOR ADVANCED SOLUTIONS TO MANAGE YOUR CRM BETTER?</h2>\r\n<a class=\"btn btn-rounded btn-white-border\" href=\"/contact-us\">Connect with us</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<style type=\"css/text\">*{box-sizing: border-box;}body{margin:0;}.gjs-dashed .container, .gjs-dashed .container-fluid, .gjs-dashed .row, .gjs-dashed .col, .gjs-dashed [class^=\"col-\"]{min-height:1.5rem !important;}.gjs-dashed .w-100{background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);min-height:0.25rem !important;}.gjs-dashed img{min-width:25px;min-height:25px;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);}.gjs-dashed .btn-group, .gjs-dashed .btn-toolbar{padding-right:1.5rem !important;min-height:1.5rem !important;}.gjs-dashed .card, .gjs-dashed .card-group, .gjs-dashed .card-deck, .gjs-dashed .card-columns{min-height:1.5rem !important;}.gjs-dashed .co