(29, 'Call Tracker Guide', 'instructions-enterprise', NULL, NULL, '<p><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><b>Option #1:&nbsp;Self-Installation:</b></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">We request you to please follow the below mentioned steps to Install the Mobile Tracker or you can&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://www.dialplug.com/dialplug/Download%20And%20Setup%20from%20Amazon.avi\"><span style=\"color:#2980b9;\">Click Here</span></a></strong> to get the&nbsp;video guide:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">You can choose from the following three options to Download the Mobile Call Tracker:</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ol style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">DialPlug Website(DialPlug.com) <b>&gt;&gt;</b> Call Tracker <b>&gt;&gt;</b> Select Call Tracker <b>&gt;&gt;</b> Scroll Down and Find Download Button <b>DOWNLOAD OUR ANDROID APP</b></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Go to Amazon AppStore and search for DialPlug-Bitrix24 and click on install</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Bitrix24 Marketplace</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">After Downloading the <b>dialplug.apk </b>file open it and click on install. After installation completion click on open.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">To set up the app the following are required:</span>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Inbound <b>Webhook URL</b></span></li>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><b>Employee&#39;s</b> Registered <b>Email Address</b> and <b>Mobile phone number</b></span></li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><b><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Please note :</span> </b>Before using the Call Tracker App please set a caller tune to inform all callers that the call is being recorded for quality and training purposes</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><b>To get the Webhook URL, Email &amp; Mobile Phone Number please follow the given steps below:</b></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><b>* Prerequisites&nbsp;:&nbsp;</b>Admin Privileges of Bitrix24 Instance and Telephony Users Details required to setup webhook URL.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><b style=\"font-size: 16px;\">In order to create the Inbound Webhook please follow the steps below:</b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Log into your Bitrix24 account as an admin. To generate webhook url Admin privileges are needed hence webhook url is provided to employee by an admin.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">On the left menu go to&nbsp;<b>More... &gt;&gt; Developer Resources</b></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Click on&nbsp;<b>Other &gt;&gt; Inbound webhook</b>&nbsp;on the top of the page</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Click on the pencil next to&nbsp;<b>Inbound webhook</b>&nbsp;and give your Webhook a name, for instance,&nbsp;<i>LeadsBridge inbound webhook</i></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Make sure&nbsp;<b>profile</b>&nbsp;is selected under&nbsp;<b>Request builder</b></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Under&nbsp;<b>Assign permissions</b>, click on&nbsp;<b>+ select</b></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Then, assign&nbsp;<b>CRM</b>,&nbsp;<b>Users</b>,&nbsp;<b>Telephony</b>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<b>Telephony(outbound calls)</b><b> </b>permissions</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Click on&nbsp;<b>SAVE</b></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Copy the URL under&nbsp;<i>Webhook </i>and paste it into Mobile Tracker&#39;s Webhook URL Box</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Webhook urlexample:&nbsp;<b>https://xyz.bitrix24.com/rest/1/ab5xyz0c0pqr2xyz/</b></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Use this&nbsp;<b>Copied Webhook URL</b>&nbsp;to configure DialPlug Bitrix24 Mobile Call Tracker</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><b>In order to create the Inbound Webhook&nbsp;</b><strong>in On-Premise version&nbsp;</strong><b>please follow the steps below:</b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Log into your Bitrix24 account</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">On the top search bar search for&nbsp;<b>Webhook</b></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Click on&nbsp;<b>Webhook</b></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Click on&nbsp;<b>Add Webhook</b>&nbsp;button in top right corner</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Select&nbsp;<b>Inbound webhook</b>&nbsp;on the top of the page</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Fill&nbsp;<b>Name &amp; Description</b>&nbsp;field with the webhook name and description</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Give the following&nbsp;<b>Access Rights Permissions</b>&nbsp;to your webhook by selecting CheckBoxes :</span>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">CRM</span></li>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Users</span></li>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Telephony</span></li>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Telephony(outbound calls)</span></li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Click on&nbsp;<b>SAVE</b>&nbsp;at the bottom of the screen</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Copy the&nbsp;<b>URL</b></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Webhook url example :&nbsp;<b>https://xyz.bitrix24.com/rest/1/ab5xyz0c0pqr2xyz/profile</b></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Use that&nbsp;<b>Copied Webhook URL</b>&nbsp;to configure DialPlug Bitrix24 Mobile Call Tracker</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong>In order to add the Employee Email &amp; Mobile Phone Number please follow the steps below:</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><b>* This is for employee use</b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Login to Bitrix24 account</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Go to <strong>Profile&nbsp;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;General</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">If <b>Contact Email</b><b>&nbsp;</b>and <b>Mobile Phone</b> is not showing there then click on edit</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Add your Email Address in Contact Email Field and Add Mobile Number in Mobile Phone Field with country code without having + (For Example - 12013458434 here 1 being the country code at the beginning of the number)</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Click on <b>Save</b></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Use this Contact Email and Mobile Phone to Setup the mobile app</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><b>Option #2:Dialplug Support Assistance:</b></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Our experts can help you setup the DialPlug Mobile Call Tracker on your Android Mobile. Please give us consent of your availability to setup a 20 minutes call over google meet/zoom/skype to install and setup Dialplug Mobile Call Tracker.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><b>Option #3: Inviting&nbsp;Dialplug team user to your Bitrix24 Instance:</b></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">We can also setup Dialplug Telephony Solution by becoming Admin User on your Bitrix24 instance. It will require:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><b>Admin Access&nbsp;</b>on&nbsp;<b><i>service-desk@dialplug.com</i></b>&nbsp;email id</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">List of Telephony users</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Based upon the option you select we would be happily available to help you setup Dialplug Telephony Solution. You may please contact us through:&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Email:&nbsp;<b><i>service-desk@dialplug.com</i></b></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Phone Number:&nbsp;<b><i>+91 9929067374</i></b></span></li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, 1, '2020-12-09 11:20:13', 0, 0, 'page', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, NULL, '2020-11-29 12:59:31', '2020-12-09 11:20:13'),
