(33, 'Bitrix Plugin', 'bitrix-plugin', NULL, NULL, '<div class=\"row\" style=\"width: 100%\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-12 margin-b-30\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:7.5pt; margin:0cm 0cm 8pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:107%\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Are you looking for a connector between your PBX call centre solution and Bitrix24 CRM ? </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0cm 0cm 8pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:107%\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Great..Our ready to use connector does this !! This connector is zero foot print plugin-play solution to sync your PBX agent call logs, call recordings and agent details like name, address and email ID to your Bitrix24 CRM. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0cm 0cm 8pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:107%\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">These details are pushed in form of leads into Bitrix24 in every 5 minutes as auto cron job. Bitrix24 Sync Engine connector is easy to use and ready to use plugin that would help you to manage your call center suits inside your CRM to track all your agent campaigns and their leads.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0cm 0cm 8pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:107%\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em><strong><a href=\"https://www.dialplug.com/vicidial_sync.php\">Click Here</a></strong></em>&nbsp;to download our Vicidial Sync Plugin</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:7.5pt; margin:0cm 0cm 8pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:107%\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em><strong><a href=\"https://www.dialplug.com/freepbx_sync.php\">Click Here</a></strong></em>&nbsp;to download our FreePBX Sync Plugin</span>